title: 144 - Worlds Largest Duck
description: Todays episode of The Pod is missing the key members Ty, Connor, and Zito who are down in Florida as Pat prepares for his third week staring on Friday Night SmackDAHN. Tone, Gump, Nick, Mitt, and Mike are joined by Jason and Bill who have become regular Friday participants. As the boys are preparing for the Draft special they get right into the Fod. Today Folder consists of all things around the internet starting off with freakishly large ducks, robot dogs, the perfect poached lunch and much more. Don't forget to subscribe to the Youtube to watch full episodes of the show and submit your questions to @thepodpmi on twitter and instagram to be featured on the PodFod. We appreciate you listening, we'll see you Wednesday, cheers.
